snippet.title: Ah Diddums (ZX Spectrum)
snippet.description: It's a bit buggy and fiddly, but still better than Schizoids, and fairly innovative for 1983. As you progress through the toy boxes your teddy's life becomes quite chaotic as more and more toys are introduced.
